<div class="modal-header">
  <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
  <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">订单-批量导入</h4>
</div>
<%= form_tag(do_import_project_path(@project), multipart: true) do %>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <ol>
      <table class="table table-condensed table-bordered">
        <thead>
        <th>产品名</th>
        <th>数量</th>
        <th>战略价</th>
        <th>单价（特价）</th>
        <th>金额</th>
        <th>备注/特殊要求</th>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        <td>必填</td>
        <td>必填</td>
        <td>选填</td>
        <td>必填</td>
        <td>必填</td>
        <td>选填</td>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <ul>
        <li>表格样式如上所示,表头（第一行）必须和上述表格一致</li>
        <li>【产品名】为产品的唯一标识，产品必须事先录入到系统当中</li>
        <li>【战略价】必须事先录入到系统当中</li>
        <li>【单价（特价）】与系统的合同价不一样时会生成特价订单</li>
        <li>表格重复上传会生成新的订单</li>
      </ul>
    </ol>

    <p style="padding:50px"><%= file_field_tag :file, accept: 'application/vnd.ms-excel, application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet' %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="modal-footer">
    <%= submit_tag '保存', class: 'btn btn-primary', data: { disable_with: "处理中..." } %>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">返回</button>
  </div>
<% end %>
